    &lt;Title&gt;Excellent Care&lt;/Title&gt;
    &lt;ScreenName&gt;Allen Davies&lt;/ScreenName&gt;
    &lt;CommentText&gt;I had a full hip replacement in Tees Valley Hospital as an NHS patient.
The treatment and care I received from admission to discharge was fantastic.
The surgeon and anaesthetist made sure I was informed and happy with how the surgery would be performed.
All the nursing staff were very cheerful and they went the extra mile to make my stay a pleasant and comfortable experience.
The physiotherapy staff were encouraging and supportive too.
As an NHS patient in a private hospital, I wasn't sure what to expect. I was amazed because my treatment was truly 5 star and given the chance again I would always opt for a referral here.
Thank you Tees Valley Hospital.&lt;/CommentText&gt;
